🟢 1. THE TAPFIELD (Birthplace of Sparks)

Biome: Soft plains of light
Color: Pastel yellow + white
Purpose: Where taps become sparks

Description

The Tapfield is an endless, glowing meadow where every tap from the child appears as a tiny spark of light.
This is where Flublets are born.

Landmarks

• The Ripple Grass — waves when tapped
• The Spark Ponds — coins float like lily pads
• The First Bounce Stone — ceremonial birthplace of Flubbo


